{"title":"ubuntu22.04安装vue","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.029Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/ubuntu22.04安装vue","updated":"2023-07-28T09:21:19.933Z","content":"<h2 id=\"ubuntu22.04安装vue\">ubuntu22.04安装vue<a title=\"#ubuntu22.04安装vue\" href=\"#ubuntu22.04安装vue\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#安装nodejs</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install nodejs </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#安装npm</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install npm</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#配置npm镜像</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"literal\">-g</span> <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#安装cnpm</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo npm install <span class=\"literal\">-g</span> cnpm</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#安装vue</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo cnpm install vue</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 全局安装 vue-cli</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo cnpm install <span class=\"literal\">-g</span> @vue/<span class=\"built_in\">cli</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"ubantu怎么让ll不显示隐藏文件","link":"2023/07/28/ubantu怎么让ll不显示隐藏文件"},"next":{"title":"vue3创建项目","link":"2023/07/28/vue3创建项目"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/